---
import PageLayout from "@layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout pageTitle="BJJ">
  <div class="paragraphs-container">
    <p>
      This is a small, tucked-away corner of my website where I track my
      training progress in Brazilian jiu-jitsu.
    </p>

    <h2>Principles</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Alignment over everything else / no scrambles or “counters”</li>
      <li>Maintain your alignment, then disrupt your opponent's alignment</li>
      <li>Control your center of gravity and momentum</li>
      <li>Continually off-balance your opponent (kuzushi)</li>
      <li>
        Use every part of all your limbs / use your head to frame, post, and
        wedge / maintain knee-elbow connection
      </li>
      <li>Address the leading edge / meet or redirect the force vector</li>
      <li>Take a dominant angle</li>
      <li>Turn your opponent’s frames into levers</li>
      <li>
        Maximize strength using lever-based control, ratchet levers, and
        internal/external rotation
      </li>
      <li>Focus your force into a small, hard surface area</li>
      <li>Advance position using placeholders</li>
      <li>Exert continuous strategic pressure against your opponent</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Solo Drills</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Technical Standup</li>
      <li>Bridge</li>
      <li>Hip Escape</li>
      <li>Inversion and Half Granby</li>
      <li>Hip Heist</li>
      <li>Hip Switch</li>
      <li>Windshield Wiper</li>
      <li>Hip Shovel</li>
      <li>Backstep</li>
      <li>Rolls</li>
      <li>Eggbeater</li>
      <li>Shin Circle</li>
    </ul>

    <table>
      <caption>Monthly Focus</caption>

      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th scope="col" style="width: 120px"></th>
          <th scope="col">Notes</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>

      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th scope="row">December 2024</th>
          <td>
            <ul>
              <li>Guard retention (starting from seated guard)</li>
            </ul>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <table>
      <caption>Phases of Guard</caption>

      <thead>
        <tr>
